name: Woolf
description:
This game was developed for the third MAD Game Jam edition, an event organized by ESMAD.

It was developed during a 43-hour period using Unity.

The theme was "everything changes at night". 

Team (TriceraTOP)
  • Bárbara Pinto (@MadDinosaur) - code
  • Eduardo Correia (@Educorreia932) - code
  • Ana Filipa Moura (@weirdnova) - art

ALT-F4 to quit the game. Cuz we didn't have the time ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
